headline.main: MRS. CHURCHILL SENDS THANKS TO BROOKLYN; Letter to Bundles for Britain Chapter Is Read at Meeting

abstract: Bundles for Brit Bklyn Chap gets thanks from Mrs W S Churchill; repts on funds and clothing sent, Jan 14-July 14
